{"tid":796710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬哈蒂爾要求中方拆除工業園區圍牆    強調工業園區不是外國領土","createTime":"2018-08-28T03:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T05:49:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ac88f7f322dc677708909fe4cfdebc9c2dfa533b","tid":796710,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞總理馬哈蒂爾表示，中國在馬來西亞一個工業園區興建的圍牆屬違法建築，應該立即拆除。馬哈蒂爾接受大馬媒體訪問時表示，工業園區有部分地方築起圍牆，並阻止大馬人進入，並不符合大馬法規，強調工業園區不是外國領土，需要遵從大馬法律，正如大馬國民在中國，會遵循中國法規一樣。馬哈蒂爾未有指明那個工業園區出問題。<br />\n<br />\n有報道就指，馬哈蒂爾所指的是啟用五年的關丹工業園區，是大馬首個國家級產業園區，距離首都吉隆坡260公里，園區內有一幅9公里長的圍牆，被當地人稱為「中國長城」。工業園區管理公司就表示，有關圍牆是園內一間中資鋼鐵廠外牆，不是包圍整個園區，但未有回應廠方是否禁止大馬人進入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1026960&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1026960%26csid%3D261_367&d=yTU0W4mAQx%2BObiGFmzoyuhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=56797d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1026960&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"63318bd0816c7f431b4c6642e1fe16540d7154c8","tid":796710,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"「一帶一路」倡議下的產業合作<br />\n<br />\n配合「一帶一路」倡議，馬來西亞與中國加強產業合作，建立了兩個產業園區，分別位於馬來西亞關丹和中國廣西欽州。在「兩國雙園」[1]的合作模式下，這些產業園區的定位是加強區域供應鏈管理，促進便利馬中兩國的貿易和投資往來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.hktdc.com/business-news/article/研究文章/馬中關丹產業園區和關丹港的前景/rp/tc/1/1X000000/1X0AA0CO.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hktdc.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Farticle%2F%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%2F%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%9C%E4%B8%B9%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%9C%92%E5%8D%80%E5%92%8C%E9%97%9C%E4%B8%B9%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%2Frp%2Ftc%2F1%2F1X000000%2F1X0AA0CO.htm&d=yTU0W4mAQx%2BObiGFmzoyuhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=28574724\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.hktdc.com/business-news/article/研究文章/馬中關丹產業園區和關丹港的前景/rp/tc/1/1X000000/1X0AA0CO.htm</a>"},{"pid":"18460219339b1a4e22cd434a45250e4d574bed0f","tid":796710,"uid":77803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"又出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7bcbe848453fd7a5e27ebf0159ed0af9a0cace","tid":796710,"uid":4661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"大馬trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a753a9fb1313133b29a6d476d75eb57b8c8123","tid":796710,"uid":17866,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1c7bcbe848453fd7a5e27ebf0159ed0af9a0cace","tid":796710,"uid":4661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"大馬trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"識跟風向玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且92歲佢無咩好怕"},{"pid":"f514395895954d2d558bebce630c79ed3ecc27bb","tid":796710,"uid":39601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"00a753a9fb1313133b29a6d476d75eb57b8c8123","tid":796710,"uid":17866,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1c7bcbe848453fd7a5e27ebf0159ed0af9a0cace","tid":796710,"uid":4661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"大馬trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"識跟風向玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且92歲佢無咩好怕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"想做返d好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9b069a789654e3aeda09c2bd678b980952071a","tid":796710,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:52:34.000Z","msg":"吳京.jpg"},{"pid":"42e1facf5ff4c82600ee79738131dd1a8f8d01d2","tid":796710,"uid":44358,"like":6,"dis