":"大馬禁碧桂園項目售盤外國客 馬哈蒂爾批非為大馬人而建<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">馬哈蒂爾上台前已形容項目「不是中國投資，而是殖民」</span>，它與其他中資參與工程是納吉布政府將國家出賣給中國的證據。當地大馬人除了抱怨有太多中國人在「森林城市」搶購單位外，還擔心其填海造地破壞環境和影響漁業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180828/s00014/1535393579927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180828%2Fs00014%2F1535393579927&d=yTU0W4mAQx%2BObiGFmzoyuhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4e91cb5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180828%2Fs00014%2F1535393579927&h=61ad7db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180828/s00014/1535393579927</a>"},{"pid":"a3c310dacee1b4203b267f7dc26f88a466289bc9","tid":796710,"uid":52006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b7d4874cf4abc726457e36070d31a960b3e4fa6a","tid":796710,"uid":4964,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cac214ca61906492562b3daf6454ea786afa201a","tid":796710,"uid":52056,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"同大馬合作起個工業園就當塊地自己有份，喺人哋國土劃租界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那真係要俾人打狗咁打先識規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"一地兩檢，早有先例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"支國最鐘意合作為名謀你d地為實，巴基爛坦，斯里蘭卡，最近仲想同一招搞美國後花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d904bf74d4364b5f5ca4c065ac29cb7817b4fb7e","tid":796710,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"馬拉趕走貪污政權後即時做嘢趕蝗殖民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fee2940989e07976bcc815812b7dafe9ec692a","tid":796710,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-